Nowadays watches are coordinated with the rest of the outfit to enhance the overall effect; accessorizing with fancy as well as simple watches has become a norm. This battery-powered watch from the house of Skagen is not only stylish but also meets the level of versatility that women expect from their accessories.

The Skagen Analog Watch for women is crafted for those who love the combination of modesty and style. The time telling device blends in with your attire as the perfect fashion accessory for any occasion. The quartz watch can be worn to parties or during casual shopping to add a zing to your day.

Body and Design

The women’s analog watch from Skagen has an attractive dial with a touch of innovation. The round dial will blow you off your mind with its sophisticated appeal. The clean dial consists of Swarovski crystals in place of the index hour markers. The depiction of the brand name in the background of the dial adds a classy appeal to the venerated timepiece. The conspicuous watch hands add a delicate charm to the watch. Even the light-coloured background adds a dainty charm to the opulent time telling device from Skagen.

Wear the ladies’ analog watch from Skagen for any occasion to any place and enjoy the versatility that it offers. The stainless steel bracelet of the watch is not only comfortable but also does not cause allergies like other strap materials do. The comfy strap is crafted in the form of a mesh and keeps your prized time wear strapped onto your wrist without any discomfort.

Your precious analog wristwatch from Skagen remains shielded from accidental damages courtesy of a stainless steel case. Stainless steel is a robust metal alloy that makes your watch sturdy and durable against wear and tear apart from adding a touch of glamour to your appearance. Also resistant to corrosion the stainless steel case will enhance the lifespan of your prized timepiece.

Functions and Other Features

The women’s analog Skagen wristwatch has the very essential water-resistance feature. With its capacity of water-resistance up to a depth of 30 m the timepiece helps prevent any damage to its functions during the monsoon. Apart from telling the time the timepiece also displays the date thus proving to be a great alternative to the calendar. If you’re looking for a watch that is simple yet elegant the Skagen women’s analog wristwatch is the perfect choice for you.
